Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是某个冬日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏是这个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:43.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢 我也要去同个地方考试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你很害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 直到考场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:18.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火都没有放开我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 我的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:26.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡衣好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:32.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇到她之前 我一直以为自己只是讨厌男生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或是单纯对恋爱没有兴趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我察觉到了这份心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是花火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
