Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.50,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)\an8}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.04,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.76,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.50,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.20,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.98,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.62,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.24,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.32,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.86,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.38,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:50.22,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}ほのかに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.48,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.12,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.56,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.20,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.72,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.04,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.08,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.50,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.04,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.76,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此简单的事情现在却最无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.50,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.20,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.98,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}无法说出口 惧怕这些话语将会毁掉现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.62,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺却仿若遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反复无常的这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.24,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放弃 还是坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.32,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永无止境的花瓣占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.86,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若然丢失了宝箱的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.38,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱紧最后一丝希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:50.22,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}将逐渐泛红的碎片藏进一声声叹息中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.48,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如果看着我 请不要移开目光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.12,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}让你看透我所隐藏的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.56,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}我不知自己能坚持到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.20,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以现在请你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.72,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}爱的如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.04,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}爱的如此恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------op -----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊 说是想要找我恋爱咨询才去了家庭餐厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却一直谈对方的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么两边都想要都不想分手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话谁都留不住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火真是纯情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后会变成孤身一人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火困了吗 要睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊床有点小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟 糟糕 要被她听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好闻的洗发水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我身上也带着同样的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢的人是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:35.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小绘？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:05.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你并不是很喜欢粟屋对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要假装喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我从花火身上感受到的违和感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我想多了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就彻底放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直注视着花火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有 喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个人不会喜欢上我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才和麦在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无语了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,选我也可以的吧
