Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:42.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我去买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从你朋友回去之后你就一直呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被没有兴趣的人告白示好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更恶心的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我说了这么恶心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人的好感…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是这么的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是难得的假日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你非要选小麦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小麦也没什么关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:54.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抢走他啊 我就只有小麦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦你不也是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:15.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦喜欢上 就觉得非那个人莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃任何一方都觉得可惜所以无法决定什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样做的话谁都留不住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后会变成孤单一人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己还不是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只会一味的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 还未明白这是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 大家都好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级 天真无邪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 芽衣 欲求不满？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是中学的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:29.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真工口 特别是早川前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然纤细却是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,带着男孩子气却有着说不出的工口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂你没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纤细却是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛吞吞吐吐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:53.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈纤细若折 胸却很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只记得那晶莹剔透的皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈是容易感到寂寞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并非寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈的身体有些冰凉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感觉不到现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却只把热情投向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:56.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 居然一个人就兴奋起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我按了门铃的 门也没锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我那啥在睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很热的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空调不都开到最猛吗 这房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 真不凑巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 怎么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 竖起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一副很感兴趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 高中？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很摇滚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,摇滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋很会学习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考试加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊怎么了别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢那个家教的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:49.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果没有暴露给任何人呢 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:50.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:53.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在思春期 让你和我交往真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为秘密拯救了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本想要把它当作逢场作戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 却是那么的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果…果然还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会 会忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:25.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…别忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是没有成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,思春期的玩具呢 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:47.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊痛 想要搞断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不懂 第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这样 试下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 总感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.22,kuzu_logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b0\c&HE685F7&\fs67.5\pos(972,639)\blur22.5\t(0,600,\blur0)}「真可爱呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是何等简单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此轻易就能触碰到麦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我却在那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为害怕而没有去接触小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 和麦在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:14.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:21.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大概是经常卿卿我我身体都变得很熟练了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有语病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得像做过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂为什么不从被窝里出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超级贤者模式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说是因为把我衣服弄脏了在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想喜欢上麦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服 洗好了还你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那衣服我蛮喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好洗掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,洗掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没洗掉的话后果很严重的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,情人旅馆什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然想去些不同的地方 我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:58.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚…晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么了这货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和男人在一起 在这种时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且感觉 不是很年轻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我工作的学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}什么啊那算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快去找位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个超级姐控的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快点走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请保密 彼此都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时间和男人在一起 我也是一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我就觉得很可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:20.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个家庭餐厅里和茜姐一起的男人 我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:20.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得他已经忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:28.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概他和我一样是茜姐家教的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起选参考书的时候遇见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 什么然后 只是原来的学生罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在深夜被叫了出去商谈些事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱是盲目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是单纯的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为何不能拥有相同的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过稍微相互挨着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有着相同心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦还是喜欢那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作为男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像这个天空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此舒畅痛快的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里哥哥会遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比我更合适的人之类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许在找着放弃的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 很热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沸腾起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是嫌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天一起的那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶嘿嘿 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是原来的学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样 什么也没有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请保密 彼此都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:33.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不必特地去烦恼吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况把那种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:41.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露给那个人的危害是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且意识到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对我哥哥的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麦对你的好意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:04.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 放学后继续 在音乐教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:10.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当时 弥漫些微香烟的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:15.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐穿着和昨天一样的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:19.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飒爽地跑开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸着 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}将胆小怯懦归咎于时代的错也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无处可归的我 找寻着愿望的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只愿成为你唇边溢出的只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}让我们一起逃离太阳系 在平行线相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}带上无法实现的希冀 以及毫无底气的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆尽 便由我开始描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影のように伸びている　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}勇気がないのは時代のせいにしてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何処にも行けない　願いの居場所を探してた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君の唇から　こぼれだす　言葉になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そんな叶わない望みも　不甲斐ない声も引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}感情全部流しきったら　描き始めてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影に今手を伸ばす　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.68,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,
